---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Poesis is the company standardizing and operationalizing the THINK layer of IT — created by Clément Cazaud."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>We make definitions generate systems.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Poesis transforms organizations — IT first — through AI-generative, agentic capabilities grounded in systemic governance. We created the Generative System Model, we build its reference implementation, and we deliver the transformation around it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Positioning</p>
      <h2>OpenTelemetry standardized RUN. Poesis standardizes THINK.</h2>
      <p class="lead">The definitions that runtimes enforce and measure against have had no open standard — fragmenting across proprietary GRC and architecture tools. Neutral stewardship is what turns a model into a standard; building the best implementation is what turns a standard into a business.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Origin</p>
      <h2>Created by Clément Cazaud.</h2>
      <p class="lead">GSM, SIE, and ITIP originate from a single thesis: systems should be <em>defined and governed</em>, not merely described. Poesis is the company that carries that thesis into practice.</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact">Get in touch →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
